===Coaches===
Notre Dame was coached by Mike Brey and his staff. In his eighth-year at the position, Brey accumulated a 142&ndash;78 (.646) record at Notre Dame before the season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cstv.com/auto_pdf/p_hotos/s_chools/nd/sports/m-baskbl/auto_pdf/0708mbbquickfacts|title=Quick Facts|publisher=University of Notre Dame|format=[[Portable Document Format|PDF]]|accessdate=2008-02-22}}</ref>
